_:Nf6392883ebf1489db2b160bfb23ce4b7 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Stephen Morgan was appointed Junior Lord of the Treasury (Government Whip) on 7 September 2025. He was previously Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State (Minister for Early Education) at the Department for Education between 9 July 2024 and 7 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>He was elected as the Labour MP for Portsmouth South in June 2017.</p>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
